Listen, you look like the sort of $(l.man) who might run a crew of your own one day. Might need a little talent. When that happens, you come to me. I'll set you up.

{{GM}}He dismisses you with a wave.{{/GM}}

{{GM}}He exhales and slowly wags his head as he speaks.{{/GM}}

Let me explain the way the world works to you. I hire someone to do a job, they do it. Then they get paid and we part happy. 

Now, you have something that I paid Coyote to get for me. That makes it mine. So you give me the pebble and we won't make any more work for Johnny Clean.

{{GM}}Mr. Delilah looks you up and down. Takes you all in. Smiles to himself.{{/GM}}

Listen, you look like the sort of $(l.man) who might run a crew of your own one day. Might need a little talent. When that happens, you come to me. I'll set you up.

{{GM}}He dismisses you with a wave.{{/GM}}

